The &lsquo;Involution&rsquo; of Hackathons A late night breakthrough on our PennApps XX Project
&ldquo;Quick, quick, Caden! Wake up &ndash; the drone is flying!&rdquo;
Half of our team had been sleeping for the past hour and a bit. Acceptable, considering the time was now 2:42 am. The drone was whirring midair in our little room, nearly getting snagged on our laptops, chargers, and free event swag. Beside us, a blackboard wall displayed a rough chalk diagram of our technical architecture.
